Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}nakushita yakusoku wa hoshi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:06.35,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}Send the lost promises to the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}omoide wa tokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.69,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}My memories won't fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.41,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yotsuba no clover sagashinagara kimi no kao
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:27.41,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I steal a glance at you as we look for four-leaf clovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,chirari nusumi mite wa me o sorasu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:33.68,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,But then divert my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,yasashii ame wa furu watashitachi no ue ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:39.08,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The gentle rain falls above our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,surechigau hito no kazu dake dramatic ni naru no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:44.59,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,as it becomes as dramatic as the number of people passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:50.13,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,kowareta taisetsu na mono to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:50.09,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll ever be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,itsuka mata aeru hi ga kurukashira
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:56.40,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,reunite with those precious things that were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:01.74,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,nokoshita kizuato ga kienai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:01.74,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,The scars that were left behind won't go away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.45,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,sorezore no basho made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:07.45,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we must depart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:11.22,hc_opening_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,mou ikanakucha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:11.22,hc_opening_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,To our own separate ways
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.66,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Six-tatami room, no bath, ten minutes by foot to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The rent is cheaper than before at 36,000 yen a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:49.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A 27-year-old wooden apartment building with a refreshing draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:52.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My room faces east and the morning sun is bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:56.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather... what in the world is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.06,0:02:00.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys sleeping in my room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.77,0:02:07.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this book said that even if we didn't have enough futons,\Nwe wouldn't freeze to death if we slept together like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.78,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Shuuei University: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a pun on the publishing company Shuueisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.78,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\shad0\fs15\fscx70\be1\fnArial\bord0.1\fscy90\3c&HE8F8FE&\c&H768280&\pos(622,56)}Published by Shuuei University\NMountain Climbing Club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:08.78,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fnAlsina Ultrajada\fs28\fscy90\fsp-0.5\bord1\be1\3c&HE7E9E9&\c&H404039&\pos(450,141)}How to {\fs32}Survive {\fs28}a {\fs32\c&H535F89&}Pinch{\fs28\c&H404039&} on the {\fs32}Mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:13.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This book is for mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:15.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And hey, just whose clothes are you wearing so casually?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't have anything left to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.16,0:02:21.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you always go along with this man's cajolery?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.50,0:02:27.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:29.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for suspecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't move... all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:35.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:36.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Daddy's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:38.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:41.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you haven't been paying any attention to me lately, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:44.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more important to you? Me or your job?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:46.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The job is more important, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:48.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san, you haven't taken a bath in a few days again, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:54.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to wear my clothes, please at least take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to. I mean, the bathhouse is expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.99,0:02:59.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I built you one that you can use for free right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:00.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to use that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:07.29,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Sign: {\be1\3c&H000000&}Former location of the washing machine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:03.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make me freeze to death. It's in the middle of winter, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone outside can see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.17,0:03:07.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And why the heck does it look intentionally dilapidated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:10.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you work for a construction company?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:12.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've been able to make something better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:15.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? I do the designs. The designs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:18.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was designed to be like an open-air bath among the palm trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.85,0:03:20.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it? Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:22.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you use it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:23.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can use the shower room at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:27.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So it is on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's on purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrificed a day off to make that for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:36.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't need to go out of your way to wind together\Ntwigs that you picked up at the park to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:37.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:42.62,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two so lively in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-san, you're going to be late for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:52.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:53.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemoto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:57.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Morita-san, that's one of Mayama's shirts again, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about every one of Mayama's shirts? Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... er...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:07.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But his clothing drawer is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:09.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's neatly packed with clean clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama is a neat freak, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:14.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I'm also wearing Mayama's underwear. Want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:18.03,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't need to show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-Morita-san! Morita-san, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm moved! Wow, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big river beyond the field of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you can't cross it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:28.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Mayama is all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:33.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita-san constantly haunts Mayama's\Nroom whether it's summer or winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.63,0:04:36.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...uses his electricity, and wears his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how hard he works, perhaps\Nhis pay gets sucked up by Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bring more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he hid his bankbook and seal properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.93,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Note: {\be1\3c&H000000&}in Japan, a personal seal is used instead of a signature in official documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:49.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but I can't suspect other people so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:51.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your thoughts are all leaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:53.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:55.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Banzai for the Iron Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.87,0:05:08.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why doesn't Mayama move from that apartment\Nnow that he's finally a working man and has money?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure his pay isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:15.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also thought about that, so I asked Mayama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:16.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:19.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's something I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:32.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something Mayama wants that I don't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:39.07,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's decided on a goal, found a way to get\Nthere, and is looking straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:41.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:43.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not afraid of becoming an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:48.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the person I fell in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:55.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was all "unya unya" and maudlin just a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:57.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Unya unya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu! Takemoto-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:00.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look! This came earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You look good in a kimono. You look like a doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, do I really look like a Hakata doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.35,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Hakata doll: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a traditional Japanese doll made from clay, usually wears a kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when did you take this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:15.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.61,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was taken in Nagano for my Coming of Age ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:18.61,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Coming of Age ceremony {\be1\3c&H000000&}is held in January of the year one turns twenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.32,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't 7-5-3?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.32,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}7-5-3 {\be1\3c&H000000&}(Shichi-go-san) is a festival for children who are three, five, or seven years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are other poses in this album!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.46,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnAlsina Ultrajada\shad0\bord0.1\be1\fad(200,0)\fs33\fscx80\fscy85\c&HB598A3&\3c&HE1E8EE&\pos(411,89)}Look at how big I've gotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:43.76,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again, touching such a delicate\Nsubject without any hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagutaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.31,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Hagutaro: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a pun on Hamtaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:53.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So Hagu-chan is also an adult now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that I wasn't the only one who\Nthought the picture was for 7-5-3.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:04.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You like sunflower seeds, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she might've matured a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.28,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's worked on something other than art...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:11.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and she's challenging herself with large projects\Nand learning one technique after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:17.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, she only spoke with Sensei and you, Takemoto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.72,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. She's changed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:27.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Little by little, but probably in a good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:32.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm just selfish for feeling lonely because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was really quiet at first, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:40.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All she did was silently look at everyone\Nfrom behind Sensei, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:43.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.87,0:07:48.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back, Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.00,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No one came to the airport to welcome me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:59.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that, you guys don't seem happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been almost a year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:04.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I mean, we didn't think you would come back all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We thought it would still be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:07.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you guys that I was coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote you guys a letter and said that even\Nthough it was sudden, I was coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your mail for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.60,0:08:15.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a letter from Hanamoto-san in Mongolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.60,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:18.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\bord1.6\shad0\fscy95\fsp-1\fs28\3c&H404039&}(When sending things overseas, let's make sure to give it plenty of time)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.12,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:43.88,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fine adult you've become.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you're gonna react?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:02.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:09.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, I was always worried that you might be sick or sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:10.87,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.33,0:09:12.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha-Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.59,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,She's returned to being a Korobokkur in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:30.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to let Mayama know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, in celebration of the safe return of\NHanamoto-sensei and Tokudaiji-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the good work, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:50.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, how joyous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:52.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the good work, Shuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:55.74,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks... Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow your nose, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:59.54,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your good work, too, Tokudaiji-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:02.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did the research proceed smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:10.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama-kun, this gathering is a celebration,\Nso let's leave serious talk for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:12.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanamoto, the deadline is this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:19.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm surprised that you came back earlier than expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it would be around March.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:28.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He would get a fever or an upset stomach,\Nand would talk in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So we ended up coming back early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:35.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I really shouldn't have taken him with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokudaiji-sensei, you meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:39.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you promise not to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:46.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh right. I brought some souvenirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.42,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.67,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayu, we match!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're called dels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:52.09,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Del: {\be1\3c&H000000&}a traditional Mongolian costume.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:54.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And let's see, what else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:58.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A doll, clothes for the doll, a hair ornament, and a bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.64,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:03.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:05.90,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally bought too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:08.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:10.15,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:11.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally makeshift.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:15.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I had to work so hard to find those.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.20,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.16,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't open without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this an outfit for Mongolian wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:26.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the hat — the proof of a champion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.21,0:11:27.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:35.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we really wanted them as material\Ndata, but they wouldn't give them to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.51,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:41.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's called the proof of a champion, it'd be\Nstupid if you could just buy it with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, we didn't have money, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:49.40,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fortunately, there was a tournament, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Tokudaiji-sensei obtained it the formal way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:12:00.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So he participated... and wrested it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's pretty! What is it, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's a morin khuur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:08.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morin khuur?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:10.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Give it to me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.47,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:20.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you smiling between Heaven and Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Sensei! Let me play it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Don't break it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.11,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How...? Why can you play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we all learn it in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.87,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure took a lot of pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:29.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, why are there so many pictures of these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.59,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're the kids of the family that took care of us over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.13,0:13:35.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In Mongolia, the older sibling takes really\Ngood care of their younger siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:41.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The little sister really likes her older brother and always\Nsticks close to him, saying, "Big Brother! Big Brother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:48.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And weren't you the one who always stuck close to that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying, "She looks like Hagu! She looks like Hagu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.23,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he broke down crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:02.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time he drank kumiss, he would get drunk\Nand scream, "Hagu!" Talk about embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:02.24,hc_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0\3c&H635514&}Kumiss: {\be1\3c&H000000&}fermented mare's milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.49,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Please stop already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Morita...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:08.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your graduate thesis coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.58,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't finished it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.13,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Tange is old, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make him worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:15.84,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Finishing your work as early as possible is key.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:22.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unacceptable for you to be counting how many days you\Nhave until the deadline and thinking that you're still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:30.02,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Those were my exact words when you\Nwere working on your graduate thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:33.31,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I sure have grown old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the day would come when I got\Nto see you lecturing your own student...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.78,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you haven't finished your work on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.45,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure haven't changed since your student days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.21,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Morita! Don't play such a reminiscent song!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.04,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:15:00.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Hanamoto-sensei would seem\Nchildish around Tokudaiji-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:04.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they've always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:07.22,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Sensei will be Sensei for the rest of his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:08.93,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:11.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei was also a student here in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.81,0:15:14.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:17.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei was just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:20.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why hadn't I thought of that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:28.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In about ten years, we'll be as old as Sensei is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:34.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adults will we be when we're in our thirties?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:42.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it might still seem far from now, today is connected\Nto tomorrow, and tomorrow to that day in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:46.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all become adults someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:51.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and people won't even think that we were also kids once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:55.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a day will come for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayama, can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:01.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...hold my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.86,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please stop. It's freaky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:06.36,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, M-Mayama-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:08.99,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Takemoto? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:10.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.96,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're all running back to the apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:18.46,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who comes in last will have to use the open-air bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mayama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:22.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a penalty game! Actually, that bath itself is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.97,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, an open-air bath sure is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So... this bath was a form of harassment, after all, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.27,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's a design piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.06,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Design...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:41.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:50.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm out of materials for my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:54.50,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can you come with me to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:56.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:03.38,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plaster, an acrylic board, some stained glass,\Na head for the burner, and a polystyrene ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.05,0:17:06.17,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can we go, like, a day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be done by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:11.89,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we'll really be finished by then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.10,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.85,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,To the art supply store, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.56,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:19.94,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.32,0:17:25.53,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-When did you become such good friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.82,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Takemoto...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:38.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is H-Hagu f-f-friends with Morita now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:40.25,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:43.63,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't know how Hagu-chan feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:47.76,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't ask me, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:56.18,hc_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you abandoning them all just because you don't want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:06.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome back, Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.34,0:19:07.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you buy what you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.55,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Morita leave already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.39,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:19.35,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:22.48,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.69,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard to keep up with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:27.19,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and my f-feet hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:32.57,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I wanted to go to the restroom,\NI couldn't tell him for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.41,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:38.24,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even remember what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.24,0:19:40.70,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't say it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:48.71,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the whole time, I wanted to\Ncome back as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.34,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.05,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd much rather be with you, Shuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.68,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like it much better!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:20:00.52,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I'm going to be with my big brother forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:01.98,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.73,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone smiles at the young girl's innocent words...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...gently looking at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:15.32,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though everyone knows that it's a wish that\Nwill disappear like snow with the passing of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:18.37,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of that, they say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.33,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:23.29,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:25.75,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to go with anyone but Shuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:26.62,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:28.92,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go together once my work is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:31.30,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with Shuu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:33.01,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.18,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hagu, here. Have some cocoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:38.14,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll warm you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:43.81,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:47.77,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mayama-san, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.44,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so spaced out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:53.65,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just caught the scent of snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:21:00.83,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although there's no way to stop what flows downstream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.91,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...let's just be ourselves for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.08,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:14.09,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pass through the town with its snowy scent\Non the way home and eat something warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.80,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then... curl up and fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:27.98,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}akanai mabuta kosutte mieru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:27.98,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I rub my heavy eyelids to reveal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:33.11,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}pastel moyou no mirai ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:33.11,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}A future in the shape of pastels
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:40.24,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}chiribamerareta kigou o tadoru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:40.24,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I follow the scattered symbols
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:44.33,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}taguri yoseta hyoujou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.41,0:21:44.33,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}As my expressions were pulled in closer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:50.08,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}nee nandakke sagashiteita mono
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:50.08,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}Say, what was it that we were looking for again?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.62,0:21:53.17,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}are wa soune itsudakke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.62,0:21:53.17,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}That's right, exactly when were those days
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:22:00.55,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}bokura ga inryoku ni sakarai nagara deatta koro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.13,0:22:00.55,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}When we used to meet, denying the attraction\Nthat was forming between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:06.47,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sore ga waltz no you dane fushigi sa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:06.47,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}It's like a waltz, isn't it? It's quite marveling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:12.69,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}sasayaku youna komorebi no kousaten de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:12.69,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}We paint away sceneries
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:18.90,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}futari waltz no youni ne mawari nagara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:18.90,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}As we waltz and spin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:25.03,hc_ending_jap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}egaki dashite yuku mono
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:25.03,hc_ending_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}Where the whispering sunlight falls through the trees and meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.75,0:22:34.79,hc_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: A sudden kiss and an unexpected parting.
